==English==

===Noun===
'''melon''' (countable and uncountable; plural: [[melons]])
#Any of various [[fruit]]s of the family [[Cucurbitaceae]] grown for food, generally not including the [[cucumber]].
#(colour) a light pinkish orange colour, like that of melon flesh.
